Kluane Red Squirrel Data

Source: R/documentData.R
redsquirrels.Rd

These data are from the Kluane Red Squirrel Project, which has been running since 1987. The data are available on Dryad at https://doi.org/10.5061/dryad.2z34tmpr3. The pedigree data are in the file `Pedigree_dryadcopy.xlsx` and the phenotype data are in the file `LRS_fordryad.xlsx`.

Usage

data(redsquirrels)

Format

## `redsquirrels` A data frame with 7799 rows and 5 columns:

personID

Unique identifier for each squirrel

famID

Unique identifier for each family. Derived from ped2fam

momID, dadID

Unique identifiers for each squirrel's parents

sex

Biological sex of the squirrel

...

Source

<https://doi.org/10.5061/dryad.2z34tmpr3>
